description: Sun OH Caxed.Charming 2-bed, 1-bath condo in the heart of South Boston! This Penthouse unit offers something unique: character, architectural charm with updated HVAC, renovated Bathroom, Private Roof-Top deck, and amazing views from a Walk-up Cupola. 743 sq ft of chic and style: with hardwood floors throughout. Updated kitchen features stainless steel appliances, wine fridge, and seating around a peninsula. The stylishly renovated bathroom features marble sink, subway tiles and hosting convenient in-unit laundry. Enjoy a private deck perfect for relaxing or entertaining with direct views, the walk-up Cupola wows with spectacular Boston skyline views and can be an office or ... a trendy bar. Located in a well-maintained three-unit building, this home sit on top of Telegraph Hill, and is close to Broadway nightlife dining while feeling residential and quiet, steps to the Telegraph Hill Park! Pet friendly, budget friendly, style forward, and ready for it's next owner. Come to take a look!
